{"tid":563213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[link有J圖]寫揮春條女好大波！！！","createTime":"2018-02-16T16:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T05:14:28.000Z","uid":40525,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba7fb0380cf7ee8cc0cfe185b0e6c6e3b8ed06d","tid":563213,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/234616_d3806059ce82f5603d7ad50da1e6ce76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F234616_d3806059ce82f5603d7ad50da1e6ce76.jpg&h=7f442cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生為揮春大灑幽默，但也有重視傳統的年輕人揮毫正經賀詞。強調番，原名為賴碧琪（Packy）的「青山不墨」寫過「係愛呀」揮春，絕對玩得，不過記者請她寫一句戊戌狗年對香港人的祝願，她大筆一揮，還是正正經經寫出了「家和人旺」。「我覺得剛過去的一年，社會發生了很多事，人與人之間有很多紛爭，希望新一年大家都和平。因為今年是狗年，即時想到『旺』字，好像狗「汪汪叫」的聲音。而只要家庭和睦，人就自然好了。」<br />\n<br />\n橫看成嶺側成峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/234649_a3c22cdaf142af8a6577bd1dde10e942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F234649_a3c22cdaf142af8a6577bd1dde10e942.jpg&h=63e27984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入來J :<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BzzzeP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BzzzeP&d=NuC2pLmyAj%2BpAB0WRKJ8Hp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bd3fbbdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BzzzeP</a>"},{"pid":"084b7f329c740cf7f7dee0d307724b70bfbc931d","tid":563213,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"普通貨仔"},{"pid":"1611e6ebd70238ffd74e9d24e9e4bfa859f8ca31","tid":563213,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"普通貨色"},{"pid":"e057821594e1e1325da98e0e311c5fc9acc3b8b9","tid":563213,"uid":140536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"波???